---
layout: base.njk
title: "Land to Land Holdings - Owner-Financed Vacant Land"
description: "Browse owner-financed vacant land with no bank and no credit check. Simple monthly payments. Work directly with the property owner."
---

{# ── HERO ── #}
<section class="hero">
  <img class="hero__bg" src="/assets/properties/LTL-001/1.jpg" alt="Open land landscape" fetchpriority="high">
  <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero__content">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow hero__eyebrow">Owner-Financed Vacant Land</p>
      <h1 class="display hero__headline">We Make Land<br>Ownership Easy</h1>
      <p class="hero__sub">No banks, no credit checks. Clear pricing, flexible options, friendly help at every step.</p>
      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a href="https://link.acrematic.com/widget/booking/NZxhdH02tv2KlHXB3vTs" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Book Free Discovery Call</a>
        <a href="/properties/" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse Available Properties</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── TRUST BAR ── #}
<div class="trust-bar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="trust-bar__inner">
      <div class="trust-item">
        <span class="trust-item__value">$0</span>
        <span class="trust-item__label">Bank Required</span>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <span class="trust-item__value">No</span>
        <span class="trust-item__label">Credit Check</span>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <span class="trust-item__value">30 Day</span>
        <span class="trust-item__label">Satisfaction Promise</span>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <span class="trust-item__value">Direct</span>
        <span class="trust-item__label">From the Owner</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{# ── FIND A PARCEL ── #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:680px;text-align:center;">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-2" style="color:var(--color-lime-tint-text);">Simple Process</p>
    <h2 class="heading-lg mb-4">Find a Parcel that Fits</h2>
    <p class="mb-6" style="color:var(--color-navy-muted);">Welcome to Land to Land Holdings! We believe everyone deserves the joy and freedom of owning their own piece of land, and we're here to help make that dream a reality.</p>
    <p class="mb-8" style="color:var(--color-navy-muted);">Explore our available properties to find your perfect match.</p>
    <a href="/properties/" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Available Properties</a>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── COMMITMENTS ── #}
<section class="section commitments-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow text-center mb-4" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">Our Commitments to You</p>
    <h2 class="heading-lg text-center mb-8" style="color:var(--color-white);">What you can expect from us</h2>
    <div class="commitments-grid">
      <div class="commitment-card commitment-card--dark">
        <div class="commitment-card__icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="14" cy="20" r="7"/><circle cx="26" cy="20" r="7"/><line x1="7" y1="20" x2="1" y2="23"/><line x1="7" y1="20" x2="1" y2="17"/><line x1="33" y1="20" x2="39" y2="23"/><line x1="33" y1="20" x2="39" y2="17"/><line x1="20" y1="20" x2="20" y2="20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="commitment-card__title">Transparent Listings</p>
        <p class="commitment-card__desc">All property details are clearly shown so you know exactly what you're buying.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="commitment-card commitment-card--dark">
        <div class="commitment-card__icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="15"/><path d="M20 12v16M16 16h6a2 2 0 1 1 0 4h-4a2 2 0 1 0 0 4h6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="commitment-card__title">Flexible Options</p>
        <p class="commitment-card__desc">Choose from easy payment plans designed to fit your budget and goals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="commitment-card commitment-card--dark">
        <div class="commitment-card__icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="15"/><path d="M20 12v16M16 16h6a2 2 0 1 1 0 4h-4a2 2 0 1 0 0 4h6"/><path d="M28 10l-4 4M12 10l4 4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="commitment-card__title">Price Match Guarantee</p>
        <p class="commitment-card__desc">Found a similar property for less? We'll match the price to ensure you get the best deal.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="commitment-card commitment-card--dark">
        <div class="commitment-card__icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="15"/><path d="M20 12v16M16 16h6a2 2 0 1 1 0 4h-4a2 2 0 1 0 0 4h6"/><path d="M12 32a15 15 0 0 1 0-24"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="commitment-card__title">30 Day Returns/Refund</p>
        <p class="commitment-card__desc">Change your mind? Enjoy peace of mind with our 30-day return and refund policy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center mt-6" style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">Small note: Land use rules (e.g. RVs, camping, mobile homes) vary by parcel and county. Always verify locally — we'll help you navigate it.</p>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── FEATURED PROPERTIES ── #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow text-center mb-4" style="color:var(--color-lime-tint-text);">Available Now</p>
    <h2 class="heading-lg text-center mb-8">Our Featured Properties</h2>
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for prop in properties %}
        {% include "partials/property-card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <a href="/properties/" class="btn btn-primary">View All Properties</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── TESTIMONIALS ── #}
<section class="section section-off">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow text-center mb-4" style="color:var(--color-lime-tint-text);">Testimonials</p>
    <h2 class="heading-lg text-center mb-8">What others are saying</h2>
    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__quote">"Stress free from start to finish"</p>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-navy-muted);margin-bottom:var(--space-4);">"Was incredibly kind, informative, and made sure everything was stress free from start to finish. Felt confident and supported the whole way through."</p>
        <p class="testimonial-card__author">B. Edris</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__quote">"Exactly what we were looking for"</p>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-navy-muted);margin-bottom:var(--space-4);">"Upfront about RV and camping restrictions. We knew what was allowed before we signed. The purchase process page walked us through each step."</p>
        <p class="testimonial-card__author">J. Martinez</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__quote">"Responsive and Trustworthy"</p>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-navy-muted);margin-bottom:var(--space-4);">"Every message got a quick, straight answer. The purchase process page walked us through it all. It was super easy."</p>
        <p class="testimonial-card__author">D. Harris</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── CLOSING CTA ── #}
<section class="cta-section">
  <h2 class="heading-lg">Your Land Is Waiting!</h2>
  <p>With a wide selection of properties across the U.S., you're sure to find your perfect match.</p>
  <a href="/properties/" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Properties</a>
</section>
